by in most parts of china speaking standard mandarin, locals always appreciate any attempt to say a few words or phrases in the local dialect, so learning a few simple greetings will help you get acquainted with the locals much more easily. in general, an understanding of or appreciation for the local speech can be useful when traveling to more remote areas. but in those areas a phrase book that includes chinese characters will still be a big help as written chinese is more or less the same everywhere. formal written chinese is for all intents and purposes the same 